UNITED SERVES MORE FAVORITE VACATION CENTERS
BY JET THAN ANY OTHER AIRLINE. For an exciting change of scenery
consider these economical holidays:
SEATTLE ... One of the biggest travel events of this or any year is the Seattle World's Fair. Through October 21, visit the
Fair, then see the Cascades, Puget Sound, Olympic Mountains and many other splendors of the great Northwest. United
serves Seattle with more jets than any other airline.
LOS ANGELES ... Visit Disneyland, the movie studios, Knotts Berry Farm ... or see Bubbles the Whale perform at Marine-
land of the Pacific. United serves Los Angeles with jets from more major cities than any other airline.
HAWAll... Enjoy a catamaran sail ... surf and sun at beautiful Waikiki Beach ... visit Pearl Harbor, Pali Pass, or the
colorful neighboring islands ... and United offers 36 jet flights a week to Honolulu from the Mainland.
NEW YORK ... Visit Greenwich Village, the many museums, the Empire State Building
Shop along fabulous Fifth
Avenue, see top Broadway plays. United offers more jets to this international gateway city than any other airline.
For further information call United Air Lines or see your Travel Agent.
